parameters.name: ExternalGUtranCell.configuredTAC
parameters.description: Used for configuration based and measurement based EN-DC setup to                                 decide if a neighbor NR cell can be used. Also used for PSCell                                 change to decide if NR cell is allowed. The configured TAC is                                 compared with the Handover Restriction List (HRL) for the UE. The                                 cell must contain at least one TAI that is not forbidden according                                 to HRL.
